00:04:00.890 --> 00:04:04.220
And I got this big
speech from my parents.

00:04:04.220 --> 00:04:07.520
About how I had to
work twice as hard.

00:04:07.520 --> 00:04:10.390
I mean, everything, I
got put on lockdown.

00:04:10.390 --> 00:04:12.400
Right? No Barbies.

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:13.700
No playdates.

00:04:13.700 --> 00:04:17.700
No super soakers with my
bro in the hot desert sun.

00:04:17.700 --> 00:04:19.490
It was like spelling
morning, noon, and night.

00:04:19.490 --> 00:04:20.790
No roller skates.

00:04:20.790 --> 00:04:22.100
They were like, no, you
can't do any of that.

00:04:22.100 --> 00:04:24.360
So, it was spelling morning, noon,

00:04:24.360 --> 00:04:26.750
and night until I was
a master at it.

00:04:26.750 --> 00:04:30.360
I remember sulking in the room that
I shared with my Mom and my Dad.

00:04:30.360 --> 00:04:32.670
