come knocking at your door.

00:05:03.730 --> 00:05:05.920
It's sort of like of when I was
allergic to my brother's cat,

00:05:05.920 --> 00:05:07.220
it would always come and sit on me.

00:05:07.220 --> 00:05:08.520
Like it knew.

00:05:08.520 --> 00:05:10.590
It hated everyone else but
