00:05:27.140 --> 00:05:28.440
How many of you are math people?

00:05:28.440 --> 00:05:29.740
I don't understand you.

00:05:29.740 --> 00:05:31.220
I'm sorry.

00:05:31.220 --> 00:05:33.550
I just, never going to get it.

00:05:33.550 --> 00:05:37.090
Anyway. As I got older,
