So, this is one of them.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:31.360
Oh, it's Calvin and
Hobbs, I'll put that up.

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:32.680
That'll be great.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:36.500
So, I personified failure
