00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:40.570
She was like a person.

00:06:40.570 --> 00:06:41.870
I could her murmuring in my ear.

00:06:41.870 --> 00:06:43.900
And she was telling
me how much I sucked.

00:06:43.900 --> 00:06:46.050
And how bad I was at everything.

00:06:46.050 --> 00:06:49.950
I'm going to explain
this in just a second.

00:06:49.950 --> 00:06:52.480
So, this whole thing
continued until college.

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:54.740
And through my very, very
first summer internship,

00:06:54.740 --> 00:06:56.040
