like really excited.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:03.590
And I failed so much that summer.

00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:05.780
It was spectacular.

00:07:05.780 --> 00:07:07.590
I was a copy editor.

00:07:07.590 --> 00:07:10.310 position:56%
