00:07:13.220 --> 00:07:15.860
I insulted reporters, accidentally.

00:07:15.860 --> 00:07:18.740
I flouted like Washington
Post grammar style.

00:07:18.740 --> 00:07:21.640 position:56%
I remember one time there was a
report who was like a real big shot.

00:07:21.640 --> 00:07:23.010
And he was calling from Iraq.

00:07:23.010 --> 00:07:26.040
And he was filing from the back
of a truck and I hung up on him.

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.340
On accident.

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:29.390
And he couldn't get back on
the sat phone to call us.

00:07:29.390 --> 00:07:31.140
And I was like, Blah.

00:07:31.140 --> 00:07:34.780
And I think my finest moment was
actually when I spelled Colombia,

00:07:34.780 --> 00:07:38.150
the country, as Columbia
the University.

00:07:38.150 --> 00:07:41.680
And it was in headline
on the front page.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:44.000
But thank God there was
a proofer who saved me

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:47.340
