00:07:47.340 --> 00:07:51.090
And I didn't have like
one of those really,

00:07:51.090 --> 00:07:53.630 position:56%
like fluffy, like sweet nice bosses.

00:07:53.630 --> 00:07:56.200
Who was like let me guide you
through your first internship.

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:57.620
No, no, no.

00:07:57.620 --> 00:07:59.940
No. He was like a hard ass.

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:03.480
And he was going to make sure
that I, but also everyone

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:06.390
in the immediate vicinity,
knew when I had failed.

00:08:06.390 --> 00:08:08.950
He had a very penetrating voice.

00:08:08.950 --> 00:08:11.720
So, failure like usual
started talking to me again.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.500
And telling me how terrible I was.

00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:17.150
And, again, my self-esteem
