down, don't take on too much.

00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:36.340
And slowly, failure became
not an enemy but a teacher.

00:09:36.340 --> 00:09:39.450
And it was one of the
longest summers of my life.

00:09:39.450 --> 00:09:41.230
When I got to the end,
I was pretty sure

00:09:41.230 --> 00:09:43.140
that my boss would either
completely ignore me

00:09:43.140 --> 00:09:45.250
and be like, please, leave.

00:09:45.250 --> 00:09:49.250
