bribed them with chocolate.

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:07.410
Lots of it.

00:11:07.410 --> 00:11:10.650
But I had been working this
night job as a copy editor.

00:11:10.650 --> 00:11:12.570
And I'd been reading
all sorts of stories

00:11:12.570 --> 00:11:14.300
