story haunted me.

00:11:39.690 --> 00:11:40.990
Because I have brothers.

00:11:40.990 --> 00:11:43.120
And I was like, what if
that happened to them.

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.970
This is not out of the
realm of possibility.

00:11:44.970 --> 00:11:46.270
What if I lived in that place.

